graph TD
    subgraph "Guardrails Regex Detector — RBAC"
        direction TB

        Note["This component defines no RBAC resources.<br/><br/>• No ClusterRoles<br/>• No RoleBindings<br/>• No ServiceAccounts explicitly configured<br/>• No Kubernetes API access required<br/><br/>The service is a stateless HTTP detector<br/>with zero Kubernetes API interactions.<br/><br/>Deployment manifests (including any RBAC)<br/>are managed externally by the platform<br/>operator or orchestrator deployment."]
